Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sei tu, Sachiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.62,0:24:15.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoro si è addormentato per strada?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.67,0:24:20.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma fino alle 21:00 era sveglio\N e parlava con Sachiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.54,0:24:22.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Lei ha un alibi di ferro.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.34,0:24:25.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Un momento!
